OL,3,CHelicopter search as four arrested
OL,4,Cafter a 'serious assault' in Swansea
OL,6,FFour men have been arrested after a
OL,7,F'serious assault' of a man on Cwm
OL,8,FRoad, in the Hafod area of Swansea.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police confirmed that four
OL,11,Fmen, a 31-year-old from Waunwen, a 49-
OL,12,Fyear-old from Gendros, a 37-year-old
OL,13,Ffrom Strand and a 39-year-old from
OL,14,FMorriston, have all been detained.
OL,16,FA Welsh Ambulance Service spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: "We were called today at 12:01pm
OL,18,Fto reports of an incident at Cwm Road,
OL,19,FSwansea.
