OL,6,F"We sent one emergency ambulance to
OL,7,Fthe scene, where the crew were
OL,8,Fsupported by a Cymru High Acuity
OL,9,FResponse Unit paramedic and an
OL,10,Foperations manager.
OL,12,F"Advanced critical care support was
OL,13,Fdelivered by the Emergency Medical
OL,14,FRetrieval and Transfer Service in a
OL,15,FWales Air Ambulance charity helicopter"
OL,17,FThe National Police Air Service
OL,18,Fconfirmed they were involved in an
OL,19,Fhour-long search for a suspect.
