OL,3,CHelicopter search as four arrested
OL,4,Cafter a 'serious assault' in Swansea
OL,6,FIt said, "At 12:40hr on Wednesday 11
OL,7,FSeptember 2024, a helicopter from our
OL,8,FNPAS St Athan base was on scene to
OL,9,Fassist South Wales Police in a suspect
OL,10,Fsearch in the Swansea area."
OL,12,FPolice say an investigation is ongoing.
OL,14,FITV News understands residents have
OL,15,Fbeen told the road is expected to
OL,16,Fremain closed and they may not be able
OL,17,Fto return home for some time.
